high_descs: Turn to the left and go to the small black table with the apples on it.
Pick up the big knife from the back of the table.
Use the knife to slice up the potato that is on the left side of the spoon.
Turn to the right and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the knife inside, and close the fridge.
Turn to the left and go back to the small black table.
Pick up a slice of potato off of the table.
Turn to the right and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the potato inside the fridge, close the fridge, open the fridge, take the potato out of the fridge.
Turn to the left and go back to the small black table.
Place the slice of potato on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a cold slice of potato on a table.

high_descs: walk to the left and turn right to go to the black shelf at the corner of the room.
Pick up the knife at the back of the black shelf.
Cut the potato on the left side of the shelf.
While still holding the knife, walk to the right and turn to the right to go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the knife in the rack and close the fridge.
Walk to the left and go back to the black shelf.
Pick up the slice of the potato on the shelf.
Walk to your right and go back to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the slice of potato in the fridge, close the fridge, wait for a few seconds, pick it up again and close the fridge.
Walk to the left and go back to the black shelf again.
Put the cold slice of potato on the black shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold slice of potato on the black shelf at the corner of the room.

high_descs: While facing the sink, turn to your left and walk towards the direction of the white table, hang a right at the small brown table.
Pick up the yellow-handled knife from the back of the brown table.
Slice the potato on the front left corner of the table.
Drop the left end slice of the potato onto the garbage bag to the left of the brown table, turn the left-most apple on its side, turn around and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and freezer doors, place the knife on the top rack of the fridge with the yellow handle towards the middle of the rack
Close the fridge and freezer doors, turn to your left and walk in the direction of the white table, hang a right at the small brown table.
Pick up the right end slice of the potato.
Turn around and walk to the fridge, open the fridge and freezer door.
Place the potato slice at the handle end of the yellow-handled knife, close the fridge and freezer door; after cooling, open the fridge and freezer door and pick up the potato slice, close the door.
Turn to your left and walk in the direction of the white table, hang a right to the small brown table.
Place the chilled potato slice between and to the front of the two apples on the brown table.
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato, refrigerate it, place it on the brown table

high_descs: Turn left and hang a right at the white table to face the small black table.
Pick up the knife with the gold handle at the very far back behind the white mug.
Slice the potato on the far left side of the table.
Turn around, hang a left at the white table, and walk to the fridge.
Place the knife inside the fridge on the top shelf in front of the dark object and close the doors.
Turn left and hang a right at the white table to face the small black table.
Pick up a slice of potato from the table top.
Turn around, hang a left at the white table, and walk to the fridge.
Place the slice of potato inside the fridge on the top shelf to the left of the knife, let it chill seven seconds, remove it and close the doors.
Turn around, walk to the white table, and turn right to face the black table.
Place the chilled slice in between two brown objects on the front right side of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled potato slice on a table.

high_descs: Turn left, walk to small table, turn right to face table.
Pick up knife from the table.
Slice the potato on the table.
Turn left, turn left, turn left, walk to refrigerator, turn to face refrigerator.
Put the knife in the refrigerator.
Turn left, walk to white table, turn right to face black table.
Pick up one potato slice from table.
Turn left, turn left, turn left, walk to refrigerator, turn to face refrigerator.
Put potato slice in refrigerator, chill, take potato slice out of refrigerator.
Turn left, walk to white table, turn right to face black table.
Put potato slice on the table between the two apples.
anns.task_desc: Chill knife and potato slice, put potato slice on small table.

high_descs: Turn left, move to the low work table at the end of the counter.
Pick up the knife at the back edge of the low work table.
Slice the potato to the left of the apples.
Turn left, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Place the knife into the refrigerator.
Turn left, move to the low work table at the end of the counter.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn left, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Place the potato slice into the refrigerator, chill it, pick it back up.
Turn left, move to the low work table at the end of the counter.
Place the potato slice on to the low work table.
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato, chill one slice.
